                                                                                            <p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/author/graziano-kratli">Graziano Krätli</a></strong> has published articles, reviews, interviews, and translations on Indian writing in English, frequently for <em>WLT</em>. He edited <em>Why Should I Write a Poem Now: The Letters of Srinivas Rayaprol and William Carlos Williams, 1949–1958</em> (2018) and two collections of Rayaprol’s selected poems and prose, <em>Angular Desire</em> (with Vidyan Ravinthiran, 2020) and <em>Random Harvest</em> (2022).</p>

